<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="harmony-n">harmony <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɑːməni/    美 /ˈhɑːrməni/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>和声：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>sing <strong>in harmony</strong>
用和声演唱</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>和睦；融洽：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The "Chinese Dream"  is a dream to improve people's well-being and a dream of harmony, peace and development.
中国梦是提高人民幸福感的梦，是和谐、和平与发展的梦。</p><footer>2013福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Only when we learn to exist in harmony with nature can we stop being a threat to wildlife and to our planet.
只有学会和大自然和谐相处，我们才能不会成为野生动植物和地球的威胁。</p><footer>人教新必修② – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>和谐；协调</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the harmony of sea and sky
海天一色</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Human life is regarded as part of nature and, as such, the only way for us to survive is to live<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (与…协调) nature.  （2015 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. in harmony with  </p></div>